-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FspN2odKHTRQ&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=68271a81\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/spN2odKHTRQ</a>"},{"pid":"481aef15346630b7f499dcee20d4cffb4d84d1f8","tid":1379241,"uid":212731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:45:48.000Z","msg":"冇選舉?<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fEd2DQ-Gm30\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfEd2DQ-Gm30&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=7ba172e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fEd2DQ-Gm30</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_bSS22hgQl0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_bSS22hgQl0&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=2e9e085c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_bSS22hgQl0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2bTip1fydfI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2bTip1fydfI&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=c9e5934e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2bTip1fydfI</a>"},{"pid":"41e913aa0395e51d5140672be7a9a218f90cfa6c","tid":1379241,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:07:02.000Z","msg":"英國管治下唔駛上街都可以向民主邁進<br />\n中國就調轉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%95%8C%E5%88%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%2588%25A5&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=d13732e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%95%8C%E5%88%A5</a><br />\n1991年《香港人權法案條例》通過後，國際法律家委員會訪港後曾指出，功能組別或抵觸人權法中「選舉權必須普及而平等」的條文，原因包括其狹窄和受限制的授權，以及部分人可以投兩票（即分區直選和功能組別），<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港英政府當時強調功能組別是過渡安排，以取代港督委任議員的做法</span></strong>，強調其臨時性質，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">長遠而言由《基本法》第68條規定終極目標是立法會所有議員由普選產生</span></strong>。[2]。<br />\n<br />\n1997年香港回歸前，功能組別的定位受到極大矚目。這源於時任<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港督彭定康在1992年進行的政制改革中</span></strong>，提出在1995年香港立法局選舉中新增九個功能組別，即「新九組方案」。彭定康並更改功能組別選舉方法、法團選票改為個人選票；<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最後功能組別符合選民資格增加至270萬人，</span></strong>實際登記人數115萬人（見2003年美國人權報告第三節[永久失效連結]、香港政策研究所報告PDF第43頁）。彭定康的這次改革被中國當局批評為鑽《基本法》漏洞，時任國務院港澳務辦主任魯平在1993年3月公開罵他是「千古罪人」。"},{"pid":"111556ab08460e66c7d6981ae3a7e3353c8fb182","tid":1379241,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:26:07.000Z","msg":"因為我未出世囉屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59f12cf8b20a143eefc14b0a4783c97305994a8","tid":1379241,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:26:59.000Z","msg":"不要說「推」，試着説「8月5號齊罷工」"},{"pid":"fb969020119a0c1f60c48b97af32065af34e863c","tid":1379241,"uid":288255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"111556ab08460e66c7d6981ae3a7e3353c8fb182","tid":1379241,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:26:07.000Z","msg":"因為我未出世囉屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:02:13.000Z","msg":"1 我地未出世/仲係小朋友<br />\n2 港英政府時期係班廢老嘅年代，就係你班撚樣唔掙取所以要班特區時代嘅年輕人企出黎，仲好意思拎港英出黎講？我屌佢老母羞唔差家？班廢老無原則可言，只要係當權者就會擁護。"}]}